title: Ep. - 490 - JAMIE MURRAY FROM REAL WORLD HOMECOMING: NEW ORLEANS 90 DAY FIANCE WITH STEFANIE WILDER-TAYLOR
description:
Jamie Murray from Real World Homecoming: New Orleans on how he was cast for MTV’s iconic show 22 years ago, reuniting with his castmates, and which cast member made the experience feel less authentic.

 

Author and podcast host (Rose Pricks and For Crying Out Loud) Stefanie Wilder-Taylor helps Kate review 90 Day Fiance, a show about long-distance loves applying for a K-1 visa to stay in the United States.
